hed: Portraits from the 2015 Toronto International Film Festival
dek: With Canada’s largest city hosting the fall’s biggest film festival, the *Vanity Fair* Hollywood team, and much of Hollywood itself, has relocated up North. See some of the festival’s top stars in these exclusive portraits from our studio.
